text: Isoya District in Shiribeshi Subprefecture. is a district located in Shiribeshi Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of 2004, the district has an estimated population of 5,949 and a density of 13.23 persons per km². The total area is 449.68 km². ==Towns== *Rankoshi Category:Districts in Hokkaido
title: Isoya District, Hokkaido
